        public String getCardBrandIdentifier()
        Returns the card brand identifier used for the payment. The following brands are supported: 
         girocard
 visa_electron
 visa_vpay
 visa_visa
 mastercard_maestro
 mastercard_debit
 mastercard_mastercard
 jcb
 discover
 diners
 american_express
        Note that the new brand id may be received at runtime. This means that a value not from the list may be returned.
